      "type": "text",
      "text": "Every message carries trace_id (Langfuse) + the security context resolved by the BFF\n(workspace_id, user_id, access_level) — workers never read these from untrusted content.\nEmbed-provider outages park the chunk in ingestion.dlq, never re-embedded with a different model\n(FR-029). 3 pods/subject in Phase 1; KEDA on consumer lag in Phase 2.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Every message carries trace_id (Langfuse) + the security context resolved by the BFF\n(workspace_id, user_id, access_level) — workers never read these from untrusted content.\nEmbed-provider outages park the chunk in ingestion.dlq, never re-embedded with a different model\n(FR-029). 3 pods/subject in Phase 1; KEDA on consumer lag in Phase 2.",
